posts.written: You will find it the easiest way to create your own font. These fonts can then be used throughout the system in other apps like iMessage, Pages, Keynote, Numbers, Word, Excel, Powerpoint,... on IOS, Mac OS and Windows. They can be easily installed and shared across devices.
